<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>nama(ḥ)stuṁgasirastuṁgacaṁdracāmara
<lb n="2" break="no"/>cāravē traiḷōkyanagarāraṁbha
<lb n="3" break="no"/>mūlastaṁbhāya saṁbhavē <g type="ddanda">.</g> namaḥ <g type="ddanda">.</g>
<lb n="4"/>śrī svasti samastabhuvanāsraya śrīpritvīvalla<unclear>bha</unclear>
<lb n="5"/>mahārājadhirājaṁ paramēsvara paramabhaṭṭārakaṁ
<lb n="6"/>satyāsrayakuḻatiḷakaṁ cāḻukyābhara
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṇaṁ śrīmatu tribhuvanamalladēvana vijayarājya
<lb n="8" break="no"/>muttarōttarābhivṟiddhipravarddhamānamācaṁdrārkkatā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>raṁbaraṁ saluttamire jayaṁtīpurada nelevīḍino
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ḻu sukasaṁkathāvinōdadiṁ rājyaṁgeyyuttamire
<lb n="11"/>yire <g type="ddanda">.</g> svasti samadhigatapaṁcamahāśabdamahā<note n="165-1">Broken after this.</note>
</p>

